Class Authentication

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.providenceuniversal.gim.Authentication
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClientMessage, Serializable

    public class Authentication
extends Object
implements ClientMessage
    The Authentication class stores credentials to be used to login, create an account or delete an account;--based on the authenticationType assigned to the particular instance. It is one of the types of ClientMessage.
